{"id":184054,"type":6,"name":"いつか阳のあたる场所で","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5f/0f/184054_cy723.jpg","summary":"自幼接受淑女教育的美丽女孩小森谷芭子（上户彩饰）生活在一个富足幸福的四口之家，不谙世事的她因与一名牛郎陷入恋情乃至获罪入狱。结束了七年刑期，芭子重返社会，对于没有任何社会经验的她来说，生活仿佛从零开始。当年因她的事件，身为社长的父亲郁郁而终，母亲（浅野温子饰）和弟弟（大东骏介饰）则选择与之断绝关系。在此艰难时刻，狱中结识的好友江口绫香（饭岛直子饰）适时施以援手。这两个各自有着不堪过去的女性相互搀扶，尽管前方黑暗重重，充满艰辛，她们仍拭干眼泪，朝着心中憧憬的光明未来前进。在此过程中，她们也温暖着他人的心灵。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>阳光照耀的未来</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>周二</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/5618\">上戸彩</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>2013年1月8日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2013年3月12日</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 爱情</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>48分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>日本NHK电视台</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>日本</li><li><span>首播地区: </span>日本</li>","collection":{"wish":2},"tags":[{"name":"日剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":639435,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639435","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639436,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639436","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639437,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639437","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639438,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639438","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639439,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639439","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639440,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639440","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639441,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639441","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":639442,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/639442","type":0,"sort":8